dc_title_s: Fire Department Response Districts Vernon County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents fire department response districts in Vernon County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This data set consists of digital map files containing current fire department boundaries for Vernon County. Boundaries were constructed though a combination of existing data provided by VTC and the 911 dispatch office of Vernon County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
